TANGMAN(6)			AmayaOS Games				TANGMAN(6)

NAME
	tangman - computer version of the game hangman

SYNOPSIS
	tangman [wordlist]

DESCRIPTION
	In hangman, the computer picks a word from the word list and you must
	try to guess it.  The computer keeps track of which letters have been
	guessed and how many wrong guesses you have made on the screen in a
	graphic fashion.

OPTIONS
	[wordlist]	Use the specified wordlist instead of the default one
			named below.

	--help		display tangman help and exit

	--version	output version information and exit

FILES
	/etc/tangman/database  Word list

BUGS
	Report uname bugs to amaya@amayaos.com

June 28, 2016
